                External
              </p>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <p>
                Used to transmit commands and receive results by applications, such as Business Intelligence tools,
                using JDBC, the Beeswax query editor in Hue, and some ODBC drivers.
              </p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <p>
                Impala Daemon
              </p>
            </entry>
            <entry>
